# ─── Inquiry form endpoint ────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Apps Script Web App URL that receives form submissions
# and writes them to a Google Spreadsheet.
#
# Setup:
#   1. Create a Google Sheet
#   2. Extensions → Apps Script → paste contents of apps-script/Code.gs
#   3. Replace SHEET_ID and NOTIFY_EMAIL inside the script
#   4. Deploy → Web App → Execute as: Me, Access: Anyone → copy URL
#   5. Paste the URL below
#
# If left empty during development, the form runs in MOCK mode:
# submissions are logged to the browser console and "succeed" after
# a fake 800ms delay — useful for UI testing without real Sheets setup.
#
# Format: https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfyc.../exec

VITE_INQUIRY_ENDPOINT=
